`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Linkdead
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

A player is referred to as "linkdead" if their character is in the game, but
the player is not connected (e.g. sometime during play, the player's network
connection has experienced a fault). A player who is linkdead, PK, but not VT,
will not be able to be attacked by other PKers.

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
